{"tid":1424252,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"【MV】警署今晚可放鬆 (原曲: Dear Jane - 經過一些秋與冬)【JVB音樂台】","createTime":"2019-08-06T15:35:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T11:55:29.000Z","uid":236333,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3377aa57680efe1d835622297696ba7ea3f18f93","tid":1424252,"uid":236333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:35:08.000Z","msg":"沙蛇三部曲最終章正式上線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rFbZ0ufrDv8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrFbZ0ufrDv8&d=JGY83BSksxqOTSpEwQoHnXvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=d44a6c6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rFbZ0ufrDv8</a><br />\n<br />\n警署今晚可放鬆<br />\n原曲: 經過一些秋與冬<br />\nMV: 占寶, Cam-man<br />\n改詞: 搞老母後面<br />\n<br />\n沙勇新好想放鬆<br />\n房間中 條啫為你動容<br />\n沙勇新不管送中<br />\n人海中 誰需用我巨龍<br />\n帶你返警署中<br />\n我兩粒花作用<br />\n進房 關燈 淫亂 鳩衝<br />\n<br />\n無謂再關心你 我在警署慰藉你<br />\n無謂性騷擾你 我在警署插入嚟<br />\n無限次舉不起 我在警署打飛機<br />\n難道我要返屋企 用政府咁慳皮<br />\n<br />\n我沙勇新不想放手<br />\n如懂吹奏 條鳩望盼口爆葉劉<br />\n<br />\n再抗爭都要抖<br />\n到我房中邂逅<br />\n做愛洗乜怕羞<br />\n別掙扎怕被扣<br />\n我賓周可比別人優秀！<br />\n<br />\n無謂再關心你 我在警署慰藉你<br />\n無謂性騷擾你 我在警署插入嚟<br />\n無限次舉不起 我在警署打飛機<br />\n難道我要返屋企 用政府咁慳皮<br />\n<br />\n沙勇新 在期待放入嚟<br />\n沙勇新 經已再扯不起<br />\n射嘢流向撻地<br />\n<br />\n無謂再關心你 我用警棍慰藉你<br />\n無謂性騷擾你 我用碌炮插入嚟<br />\n無限次舉不起 我用手扣打飛機<br />\n難道做愛返屋企 喔～<br />\n無謂勸我返屋企 用政府最慳皮<br />\n差館裡沒數記 耶～<br />\n<br />\n聽到周街反送中<br />\n回憶中 條啫又要洩慾<br />\n<br />\n同場加映沙蛇三部曲第一二章<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n《警署只得我共你》<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lKYcafqBi84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlKYcafqBi84&d=JGY83BSksxqOTSpEwQoHnXvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=8c405a11\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lKYcafqBi84</a><br />\n《只想將警棍塞進㝫》<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6EcOoCiCfhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6EcOoCiCfhk&d=JGY83BSksxqOTSpEwQoHnXvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=1487d318\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6EcOoCiCfhk</a>"},{"pid":"afcb26cbd638df317eb44e6fbb0e717d404cb353","tid":1424252,"uid":100714,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:36:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />痴撚線"},{"pid":"6bdfd5762ddec2d1ebfe59cdb002c75b8312a626","tid":1424252,"uid":274180,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:59:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一幕手機睇fb嗰到已經笑到仆街<br />\n個尾仲撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">今次真係唔輸得 辱警罪過左我地實有排坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"c82f58532f83099ea3e5f87d5115877af0772dec","tid":1424252,"uid":203845,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:02:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前線手足睇下輕鬆下<br />\n而家嘅香港太沉重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d5ab352b51f1484b42e9b5d911741ed042f4042","tid":1424252,"uid":236333,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6bdfd5762ddec2d1ebfe59cdb002c75b8312a626","tid":1424252,"uid":274180,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:59:54.000Z","msg":"<im